marketing: Shell HD Ultra ELC N Antifreeze/Coolant Pre-Diluted 55/45 is a nitrited extended life ethylene glycol coolant for heavy duty diesel and natural gas-powered engines. Shell HD Ultra ELC N Antifreeze/Coolant Pre-Diluted 55/45 contains OAT corrosion inhibitor technology plus nitrite and molybdate. The product is free of amines, borates, nitrates, phosphates and silicates. Shell HD Ultra ELC N Antifreeze/Coolant Pre-Diluted 55/45 provides excellent corrosion protection of HD engines and cooling system components without the use of supplemental coolant additives (SCAs). Shell HD Ultra ELC N Antifreeze/Coolant Pre-Diluted 55/45 is premixed and ready to use. It requires no further dilution.
